# build libc with gcc
- kernel headers
- gcc 
- The GNU C Library cannot be compiled in the source directory. You must build it in a separate build directory

# steps

## download glibc source code

## configure glibc
```
# for native build
cd glibc_build
../glibc_src/configure --prefix=$GLIBC_INSTALL_DIR --with-headers=$KERNEL_HEADERS 
```

# references
1. https://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_mono/libc.html#Installation


